13:6-9](../../../bib/kjv/luk013.htm#006).md). The withered fig tree is a
parabolic miracle concerning Israel. ([Luk
13:6-9](../../../bib/kjv/luk013.htm#006).md).

Compare ([Mat 24:32](../../../bib/kjv/mat024.htm#032).md); ([Mat
24:33](../../../bib/kjv/mat024.htm#033).md);

a prophecy that Israel shall again bud.

